@startuml 15-proof-loop
title Full Proof Loop — Human Input to Verified Result

skinparam shadowing false

start
:Human / operator input;
:Form / API validates shape;
:dteam builds canonical process challenge;
:dteam compiles semantic motion\n(predicates: requires / law / cap / scenario);

:dteam-unios adapter submits motion;
:unios binds law / capability / scenario;
:unios scope planner selects typed hot handle\n(monomorphized by tier + receipt mode);

:unibit API receives admitted handle;
:Nightly Rust monomorphized kernel runs;
:Branchless mask algebra\n(cargo-asm verified);
:Operates on pinned UniverseBlock + UniverseScratch;

:Emit sparse ΔU;
:Emit receipt fragment\n(R_{t+1} = mix(R_t, I, ΔU));

:unios Supervisor observes delta;
:unios finalizes UReceipt (tier-appropriate);
:dteam public receipt returned;

:dteam projects UProjection\n(disposable derived view);

:Auditor / human verifies receipt\n(independent replay);

if (Replay matches receipt?) then (yes)
  :Verified: TRUE;
else (no)
  :Verified: FALSE;
endif

stop

note right
  Authority lives in ΔU + UReceipt.
  Projections are disposable.
  Verification is independent of implementation.
end note

@enduml
